                        <note>Text of Mommsen in CIL</note>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                        <note>Bivona states that interpunct only visible after Lucia in line 1, but Mommsen records them throughout on the basis of autopsy and it is apparent that they are faintly visible in the photograph but lacking in paint (which may be modern?)</note>
                    </app>
